Class MembershipState

java.lang.Object
  DDS.MembershipState

public final class MembershipState
extends java.lang.Object

The MembershipState class represents an enumeration of the possible states of a member of a Selection.

Field Detail

_UNDEFINED_MEMBERSHIP

public static final int _UNDEFINED_MEMBERSHIP
This option indicates that the concerned object has an undefined membership state in relation to the selection. Meaning it could already be a member or be a newly inserted member.
